room_title: Escape room "Pixel Panic: Claim Your Glory!" by Escape Adventures in Baltimore
room_description:
What a day! You went to Bob's Arcade and you got the high score on your favorite game! Furious, Bob grabbed the photo of the high score and threw it in his safe, locked up tight and out of sight! He couldn't stand you having the high score!
Well, you have a plan! Gathering your friends, you break into Bob's Arcade one hour before it opens. You'll show him! In one hour, you have to find a way to get into the safe, collect your photo, and get back out. Can you steal back your high score photo AND get out before Bob gets in and catches you?
